ChurchofJesusChrist.org.</p></div><span style=-ms-grid-row:15>8.</span><div style=-ms-grid-row:15><p data-aid=143140806 id=note8_p1>See <a class="" href=/#note8>Exodus 34:28</a>; <a class="" href=/#note8>2 Samuel 12:16</a>; <a class="" href=/#note8>Ezra 10:6</a>; <a class="" href=/#note8>Nehemiah 1:4</a>; <a class="" href=/#note8>Esther 4:16</a>; <a class="" href=/#note8>Isaiah 58:3</a>; <a class="" href=/#note8>Daniel 9:3</a>; <a class="" href=/#note8>Joel 2:12</a>.</p></div><span style=-ms-grid-row:17>9.</span><div style=-ms-grid-row:17><p data-aid=143140807 id=note9_p1><a class="" href=/#note9>Isaiah 58:6</a>; emphasis added.</p></div><span style=-ms-grid-row:19>10.</span><div style=-ms-grid-row:19><p data-aid=143140808 id=note10_p1><a class="" href=/#note10>1 Corinthians 7:5</a>.</p></div><span style=-ms-grid-row:21>11.</span><div style=-ms-grid-row:21><p data-aid=143140809 id=note11_p1><a class="" href=/#note11>Matthew 17:21</a>; emphasis added.</p></div><span style=-ms-grid-row:23>12.</span><div style=-ms-grid-row:23><p data-aid=143140810 id=note12_p1>Russell M. Nelson, in “<a class="" href=/#note12>Prophet Invites All to Fast and Pray for Relief from COVID-19</a>,” Mar. 26, 2020, newsroom.ChurchofJesusChrist.org.</p></div><span style=-ms-grid-row:25>13.</span><div style=-ms-grid-row:25><p data-aid=143140811 id=note13_p1><a class="" href=/#note13>Alma 26:35</a>.</p></div><span style=-ms-grid-row:27>14.</span><div style=-ms-grid-row:27><p data-aid=143140812 id=note14_p1>See <a class="" href=/#note14>Alma 17:3</a>.</p></div></section></div></div></aside></div></main><div><div><script type=text/javascript> var channel = 'www.lds.org'; var pageName = 'www.lds.org:""'; var locale = '"eng"'; var LDS = LDS || { }; LDS.track = LDS.track || { }; LDS.track.pageName = pageName; LDS.track.channel = channel; LDS.track.prop35 = locale; if (typeof(searchType) !== 'undefined' && typeof(searchResults) !== 'undefined') {    LDS.track.eVar53=searchType;    LDS.track.eVar56=searc